strings: <voice_0x01001CC6><se_high>Media princess: What do you like in these meetings<hero>?
<voice_0x01001CC7><se_high>Media princess: I'm late, but there's something I want to talk to you about. But I will have to grow up...
<voice_0x01001CC8><se_high>Media princess: If you've got a dream, don't miss it!
<voice_0x01001CC9><se_high>Media princess: Do you think it affects the well water?
<voice_0x01001CCA><se_high>Media princess: I really want to tell you the story about Prince Charming, but there is no magic.
<voice_0x01001C6D><se_high>Media princess: But... Do you think that will change after the wedding?
<voice_0x01001C6F><se_high>Media princess: <hero> I know, I know, I was selfish when I was younger.
<voice_0x01001C71><se_high>Media princess: Prince Charles' condition is improving...
